          "text": "The essence rocks are near the altars to the south. Mine the essence, then use it at the air altar."
        },
        {
          "id": "quest_complete",
          "text": "Wonderful! You've grasped the fundamentals of runecrafting. The arcane arts are now open to you. Here's your reward.",
          "effect": "completeQuest:rune_mysteries"
